    {
      "comment": "Introduction to the concept of a prompt as a conversation starter.",
      "speech": "Talking to an AI isn't just about asking a question; it's about starting a conversation. The secret to unlocking its potential isn't a magic button—it's the prompt.",
      "elevenlabs": "[warmly welcoming] Talking to an AI isn't just about asking a question; [thoughtfully] it's about starting a conversation. The secret to unlocking its potential isn't a magic button—[emphasized] it's the prompt.",
      "duration": "10.56s",
