    {
      "comment": "Example of a generic prompt and its limitations.",
      "speech": "Think of a prompt as your instruction. If you give a vague instruction, like 'Give me gift ideas,' the AI will give you a vague, generic response. It's just following the easiest, most common patterns it knows.",
      "elevenlabs": "[patiently] Think of a prompt as your instruction. [matter-of-fact] If you give a vague instruction, like 'Give me gift ideas,' the AI will give you a vague, generic response. [short pause] It's just following the easiest, most common patterns it knows.",
      "duration": "13.16s",
      "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <title>Prompt</title>\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Semi+Condensed:wght@600&family=Figtree:wght@400;600&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <style>\n    /* ── Boilerplate: do not modify ── */\n    :root {\n      --color-teal:           #0093A4;\n      --color-purple:         #8C52BA;\n      --color-aqua:           #3CFFF7; /* AI features only */\n      --color-error:          #E02D16;\n      --color-warning:        #F9CB28;\n      --color-success:        #3EA33E;\n      --color-info:           #1892E3;\n      --color-text-primary:   #292F36;\n      --color-text-secondary: #4C5661;\n      --color-gray-light:     #F7F8FA;\n      --color-gray-medium:    #D1D4D8;\n      --color-gray-dark:      #5F6872;\n    }\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n    html, body {\n      width: 1600px;\n      height: 900px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      transform-origin: top left;\n      font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;\n      color: var(--color-text-primary);\n    }\n    /* ── End boilerplate ── */\n\n    body {\n      background: linear-gradient(150deg, var(--color-purple) 0%, #5a2d8a 100%);\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n    }\n\n    .card {\n      background: #ffffff;\n      border-radius: 24px;\n      box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n      padding: 56px 80px;\n      max-width: 1440px;\n      width: 100%;\n      text-align: center;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 20px;\n      animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease both;\n    }\n\n    .big-text {\n      font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed', sans-serif;\n      font-size: 112px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      color: var(--color-text-primary);\n      line-height: 1.1;\n    }\n\n    .secondary {\n      font-size: 32px;\n      font-weight: 400;\n      color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n      line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n\n    @keyframes fadeIn {\n      from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.96); }\n      to   { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"card\">\n    <blockquote class=\"big-text\">Prompt</blockquote>\n    <p class=\"secondary\">Your instruction that shapes how AI responds.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Boilerplate: do not modify -->\n  <script>\n    function resize() {\n      document.documentElement.style.transform = `scale(${window.innerWidth / 1600})`;\n    }\n    window.addEventListener('resize', resize);\n    resize();\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
