    {
      "comment": "Demonstration of experimentation by adding specific details.",
      "speech": "But here's where the fun starts: Experimentation. What happens if you change the input? Instead of just 'gifts,' you add specifics—like a 15-year-old artist who loves watercolor. By changing the prompt, you force the AI to find new, more relevant patterns.",
      "elevenlabs": "[excited] But here's where the fun starts: Experimentation. [curiously] What happens if you change the input? Instead of just 'gifts,' you add specifics—[deliberate] like a 15-year-old artist who loves watercolor. By changing the prompt, you force the AI to find new, more relevant patterns.",
      "duration": "18.36s",
      "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <title>Vague vs. Specific Prompt</title>\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Semi+Condensed:wght@600&family=Figtree:wght@400;600&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <style>\n    /* ── Boilerplate: do not modify ── */\n    :root {\n      --color-teal:           #0093A4;\n      --color-purple:         #8C52BA;\n      --color-aqua:           #3CFFF7; /* AI features only */\n      --color-error:          #E02D16;\n      --color-warning:        #F9CB28;\n      --color-success:        #3EA33E;\n      --color-info:           #1892E3;\n      --color-text-primary:   #292F36;\n      --color-text-secondary: #4C5661;\n      --color-gray-light:     #F7F8FA;\n      --color-gray-medium:    #D1D4D8;\n      --color-gray-dark:      #5F6872;\n    }\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n    html, body {\n      width: 1600px;\n      height: 900px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      transform-origin: top left;\n      font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;\n      background: var(--color-gray-light);\n      color: var(--color-text-primary);\n    }\n    /* ── End boilerplate ── */\n\n    body {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n    }\n\n    .header {\n      height: 140px;\n      padding: 0 64px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      background: var(--color-gray-light);\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n      animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease both;\n    }\n\n    .heading {\n      font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed', sans-serif;\n      font-size: 64px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      color: var(--color-text-primary);\n      line-height: 1.1;\n      border-left: 8px solid var(--color-teal);\n      padding-left: 24px;\n    }\n\n    .svg-area {\n      flex: 1;\n      padding: 24px 64px 48px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      min-height: 0;\n      animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease 0.1s both;\n    }\n\n    .svg-area svg {\n      width: 100%;\n      height: 100%;\n    }\n\n    /* ── no-title modifier ── */\n    body.no-title .header { display: none; }\n    body.no-title .svg-area { padding-top: 48px; }\n\n    @keyframes fadeIn {\n      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }\n      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"no-title\">\n  <!-- Sequence: ThePrompt | user-prompt=#0093A4 | ai-processing=#8C52BA | output=#F7F8FA/#D1D4D8 | arrows=2px #292F36 -->\n\n  <div class=\"header\">\n    <h1 class=\"heading\">Vague vs. Specific Prompt</h1>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"svg-area\">\n    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 820\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <defs>\n        <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n          <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#292F36\"/>\n        </marker>\n      </defs>\n\n      <!-- ══ ROW 1: VAGUE PROMPT ══ -->\n\n      <!-- Row 1 label pill -->\n      <rect x=\"560\" y=\"24\" width=\"320\" height=\"44\" rx=\"22\" fill=\"#D1D4D8\"/>\n      <text x=\"720\" y=\"52\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"20\"\n            font-weight=\"600\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#5F6872\" letter-spacing=\"1\">VAGUE PROMPT</text>\n\n      <!-- Box 1 — teal (user prompt) -->\n      <rect x=\"80\" y=\"85\" width=\"320\" height=\"185\" rx=\"18\" fill=\"#0093A4\"/>\n      <text x=\"240\" y=\"163\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"26\"\n            font-weight=\"600\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\">\"Give me</text>\n      <text x=\"240\" y=\"194\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"26\"\n            font-weight=\"600\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\">gift ideas\"</text>\n      <text x=\"240\" y=\"234\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"17\"\n            text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.8)\">vague instruction</text>\n\n      <!-- Arrow 1→2 row 1 -->\n      <line x1=\"402\" y1=\"177\" x2=\"488\" y2=\"177\" stroke=\"#292F36\" stroke-width=\"2\"\n            marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n\n      <!-- Box 2 — purple (AI) -->\n      <rect x=\"500\" y=\"85\" width=\"320\" height=\"185\" rx=\"18\" fill=\"#8C52BA\"/>\n      <text x=\"660\" y=\"168\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"36\"\n            font-weight=\"600\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\">AI</text>\n      <text x=\"660\" y=\"210\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"17\"\n            text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.8)\">finds common patterns</text>\n\n      <!-- Arrow 2→3 row 1 -->\n      <line x1=\"822\" y1=\"177\" x2=\"908\" y2=\"177\" stroke=\"#292F36\" stroke-width=\"2\"\n            marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n\n      <!-- Box 3 — gray (output) -->\n      <rect x=\"920\" y=\"85\" width=\"440\" height=\"185\" rx=\"18\" fill=\"#F7F8FA\" stroke=\"#D1D4D8\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n      <text x=\"1140\" y=\"156\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"22\"\n            font-weight=\"600\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#292F36\">Generic gift list</text>\n      <text x=\"1140\" y=\"185\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"17\"\n            text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#4C5661\">• Books  • Candles  • Gift cards</text>\n      <text x=\"1140\" y=\"213\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"17\"\n            text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#4C5661\">• Socks  • Chocolates  ...</text>\n      <text x=\"1140\" y=\"243\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"15\"\n            text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#5F6872\">not very helpful</text>\n\n      <!-- ══ DIVIDER ══ -->\n      <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"336\" x2=\"1380\" y2=\"336\" stroke=\"#D1D4D8\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,6\"/>\n      <!-- VS badge -->\n      <rect x=\"670\" y=\"318\" width=\"100\" height=\"40\" rx=\"20\" fill=\"#292F36\"/>\n      <text x=