,0.8)\">finds relevant patterns</text>\n\n      <!-- Arrow 2→3 row 2 -->\n      <line x1=\"822\" y1=\"520\" x2=\"908\" y2=\"520\" stroke=\"#292F36\" stroke-width=\"2\"\n            marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n\n      <!-- Box 3 — gray (specific output) -->\n      <rect x=\"920\" y=\"428\" width=\"440\" height=\"185\" rx=\"18\" fill=\"#F7F8FA\" stroke=\"#0093A4\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n      <text x=\"1140\" y=\"496\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"22\"\n            font-weight=\"600\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#292F36\">Relevant suggestions</text>\n      <text x=\"1140\" y=\"525\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"17\"\n            text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#4C5661\">• Watercolor sketchbook</text>\n      <text x=\"1140\" y=\"551\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"17\"\n            text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#4C5661\">• Art supply subscription</text>\n      <text x=\"1140\" y=\"577\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"17\"\n            text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#4C5661\">• Online painting class</text>\n      <text x=\"1140\" y=\"597\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"15\"\n            text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#0093A4\">much more helpful!</text>\n\n      <!-- ══ CAPTION ══ -->\n      <text x=\"720\" y=\"680\" font-family=\"Figtree, sans-serif\" font-size=\"22\"\n            text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#4C5661\">Specific details help AI find more relevant patterns.</text>\n\n    </svg>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Boilerplate: do not modify -->\n  <script>\n    function resize() {\n      document.documentElement.style.transform = `scale(${window.innerWidth / 1600})`;\n    }\n    window.addEventListener('resize', resize);\n    resize();\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
