    {
      "comment": "Explanation of the iteration loop and refinement process.",
      "speech": "This is iteration. It's rarely one-and-done. You observe the first response, see what's missing, and refine. It's like coaching a teammate. You might say, 'That's good, but keep it under thirty dollars,' or even add an image to show exactly the style you're looking for.",
      "elevenlabs": "[thoughtful] This is iteration. It's rarely one-and-done. [patiently] You observe the first response, see what's missing, and refine. It's like coaching a teammate. You might say, [encouraging] 'That's good, but keep it under thirty dollars,' or even add an image to show exactly the style you're looking for.",
      "duration": "18.01s",
      "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <title>Iteration</title>\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Semi+Condensed:wght@600&family=Figtree:wght@400;600&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <style>\n    /* ── Boilerplate: do not modify ── */\n    :root {\n      --color-teal:           #0093A4;\n      --color-purple:         #8C52BA;\n      --color-aqua:           #3CFFF7; /* AI features only */\n      --color-error:          #E02D16;\n      --color-warning:        #F9CB28;\n      --color-success:        #3EA33E;\n      --color-info:           #1892E3;\n      --color-text-primary:   #292F36;\n      --color-text-secondary: #4C5661;\n      --color-gray-light:     #F7F8FA;\n      --color-gray-medium:    #D1D4D8;\n      --color-gray-dark:      #5F6872;\n    }\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n    html, body {\n      width: 1600px;\n      height: 900px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      transform-origin: top left;\n      font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;\n      background: var(--color-gray-light);\n      color: var(--color-text-primary);\n    }\n    /* ── End boilerplate ── */\n\n    body {\n      display: flex;\n      padding: 48px 64px;\n      gap: 48px;\n      align-items: stretch;\n    }\n\n    .col-quote {\n      flex: 1;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      justify-content: center;\n      gap: 28px;\n      border-left: 10px solid var(--color-teal);\n      padding-left: 40px;\n      animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease both;\n    }\n\n    .heading {\n      font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed', sans-serif;\n      font-size: 96px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      color: var(--color-text-primary);\n      line-height: 1.05;\n    }\n\n    .subheading {\n      font-size: 36px;\n      font-weight: 400;\n      color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n      line-height: 1.4;\n    }\n\n    .col-image {\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 12px;\n      animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease 0.1s both;\n    }\n\n    .image {\n      height: 100%;\n      aspect-ratio: 9 / 16;\n      object-fit: cover;\n      border-radius: 16px;\n    }\n\n    @keyframes fadeIn {\n      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }\n      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"col-quote\">\n    <h1 class=\"heading\">Iteration</h1>\n    <p class=\"subheading\">Observe, refine, repeat — like coaching a teammate.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"col-image\">\n    <img src=\"C:\\Users\\Dan\\Documents\\Claude\\ed-json-video-player\\json-video-player\\generation\\tools\\generated-images\\generated_image_6a87d9af-8808-489d-ba52-966aa3d25997.png\" alt=\"Coach giving encouraging feedback to a player on a bench\" class=\"image\">\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Boilerplate: do not modify -->\n  <script>\n    function resize() {\n      document.documentElement.style.transform = `scale(${window.innerWidth / 1600})`;\n    }\n    window.addEventListener('resize', resize);\n    resize();\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
