    {
      "comment": "Recognizing patterns and using different personas for outputs.",
      "speech": "As you iterate, you'll start to recognize patterns in how the AI responds. You'll learn that adding details about emotions, specific topics, or even a 'persona' like a debate partner changes the 'flavor' of the output entirely.",
      "elevenlabs": "[reflective] As you iterate, you'll start to recognize patterns in how the AI responds. [insightful] You'll learn that adding details about emotions, specific topics, or even a 'persona' like a debate partner changes the 'flavor' of the output entirely.",
      "duration": "13.97s",
      "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <title>Add More Detail</title>\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Semi+Condensed:wght@600&family=Figtree:wght@400;600&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <style>\n    /* ── Boilerplate: do not modify ── */\n    :root {\n      --color-teal:           #0093A4;\n      --color-purple:         #8C52BA;\n      --color-aqua:           #3CFFF7; /* AI features only */\n      --color-error:          #E02D16;\n      --color-warning:        #F9CB28;\n      --color-success:        #3EA33E;\n      --color-info:           #1892E3;\n      --color-text-primary:   #292F36;\n      --color-text-secondary: #4C5661;\n      --color-gray-light:     #F7F8FA;\n      --color-gray-medium:    #D1D4D8;\n      --color-gray-dark:      #5F6872;\n    }\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n    html, body {\n      width: 1600px;\n      height: 900px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      transform-origin: top left;\n      font-family: 'Figtree', sans-serif;\n      background: var(--color-gray-light);\n      color: var(--color-text-primary);\n    }\n    /* ── End boilerplate ── */\n\n    body {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n    }\n\n    .header {\n      height: 140px;\n      padding: 0 64px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      background: var(--color-gray-light);\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n      animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease both;\n    }\n\n    .heading {\n      font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed', sans-serif;\n      font-size: 64px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      color: var(--color-text-primary);\n      line-height: 1.1;\n      border-left: 8px solid var(--color-teal);\n      padding-left: 24px;\n    }\n\n    .main {\n      flex: 1;\n      display: flex;\n      gap: 48px;\n      padding: 32px 64px 48px;\n      align-items: stretch;\n      min-height: 0;\n    }\n\n    .col-bullets {\n      flex: 1;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      justify-content: center;\n      animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease 0.1s both;\n    }\n\n    .bullets {\n      list-style: none;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 32px;\n    }\n\n    .bullets li {\n      font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed', sans-serif;\n      font-size: 52px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      color: var(--color-text-primary);\n      line-height: 1.1;\n      border-left: 6px solid var(--color-purple);\n      padding-left: 24px;\n    }\n\n    .col-image {\n      flex-shrink: 0;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease 0.15s both;\n    }\n\n    .image {\n      height: 100%;\n      aspect-ratio: 9 / 16;\n      object-fit: cover;\n      border-radius: 16px;\n    }\n\n    @keyframes fadeIn {\n      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }\n      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"header\">\n    <h1 class=\"heading\">Add More Detail</h1>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"main\">\n    <div class=\"col-bullets\">\n      <ul class=\"bullets\">\n        <li>Emotions and tone</li>\n        <li>Specific topics</li>\n        <li>A persona or role</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"col-image\">\n      <img src=\"C:\\Users\\Dan\\Documents\\Claude\\ed-json-video-player\\json-video-player\\generation\\tools\\generated-images\\generated_image_1844c036-b137-4e6d-9999-90903deca6b1.png\" alt=\"Person with thought bubbles showing different roles: debate partner, creative writer, scientist\" class=\"image\">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Boilerplate: do not modify -->\n  <script>\n    function resize() {\n      document.documentElement.style.transform = `scale(${window.innerWidth / 1600})`;\n    }\n    window.addEventListener('resize', resize);\n    resize();\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
